[style name="res://Dialogue/Styles/CozyPersonaVN.tres"]
The SCHOOL BELL rings.
[signal arg="sfx:school_bell"]
[background arg="res://Art/Backgrounds/mayas_room.png" fade="0.7"]
A calendar hangs above Maya's desk.
SCRATCH.
One day is crossed out.
SCRATCH.
Another day disappears.
Assignments and lecture notes begin piling up on her desk.
SCRATCH.
Another day.
Coffee cups now sit beside unfinished reviewers and textbooks.
Maya types on her laptop while scribbling notes at the same time.
Maya studies alone, surrounded by books and printed notes.
She checks the time, sighs, and continues working.
SCRATCH.
Another day is crossed out.
The calendar slowly fills with marked dates as the workload continues to grow.
Maya stares at her long to-do list before taking a deep breath and getting back to work.
Maya studies alone.
Her eyes move across pages of notes.
Her phone, resting beside her reviewer, suddenly vibrates.
Every few moments, she instinctively glances at the screen.
She returns to reading.
A few lines later, she checks it again.
Still nothing.
Suddenly...
A text notification appears.
A message from Ethan.
Maya glances at it.
join Ethan (neutral) right [animation="Instant In"]
Ethan: "Still alive?"
Maya smiles.
join Maya (neutral) left [animation="Instant In"]
Maya: "Barely."
